cs.SE, cs.CV, cs.PL, cs.SY, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category as the paper discusses a method for testing software and addresses the oracle problem. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper specifically mentions image processing software and proposes an object-based metamorphic testing approach through image structuring. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper may discuss programming languages used for implementing the proposed method. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the System Under Test (SUT) and its control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the use of metamorphic testing in AI systems.
